'''Ursu amellal''' neɣ '''Ursu asafayku''', ([[Assaɣ usnan]]: ''Ursus maritimus''), d [[talmest]] n [[ursun|ursunen]] yeṭṭafaren [[asmil]] n [[timsiffatin|temsiffatin]]  seg [[tawacult (tasnudert)|twacult]] n [[iɣelɣalen]], Yettidir deg [[tama|tamiwin]] [[Anezwu agersan|tugersanin]] id yezzin ɣef [[Agaraw Arkti|Ugaraw Arkti]] (deg ugafa n [[Kanada]], [[Rrus]] d [[Skundinavya]]. Ursu amellal d yiwen seg yiɣersiwen yeṭṭafaren [[tafesna]] n [[timseksumin]] imeqranen akk deg umaḍal imi [[tiddi|tiddi-ynes]] tezmer ad yaweḍ ɣer 2,5m deg teflel (mara ad ibedd ɣef yiḍarren-nnis udfiren), Ma d [[azuk]]-is azal n 7 n yiqenṭaren. 

[[Tafekka]] n wursu-a d tamellalt s umata, yerna anect-a [[tallalt|yettalel-it]] ad yessedreg iman-nnes deg temlel-nni n [[adfel|wedfel]] d [[Agris|wegris]] aydeg yettiddir. Seg tama niḍen, aglim-is d azuran yerna d win ay yettarran fell-as asemmiḍ. Ursu amellal [[ardab|ireddeb]] deg waman isemmaḍen n Ugaraw Arkti, am wakken ay yezmer ad yazzel s tɣawla d tameqrant ɣef wegris. Yesɛa anzad ula ddaw yiḍarren-nnes i wakken ur ittecceḍ deg wedfel, yerna yettṣeyyid iselman ed yidemriyen


